<a href="http://www.w3.org/Consortium/Translation">translations</a>, <a href="http://www.w3.org/Style/CSS/members">working group</a>

</p><p class="map-also"><a href="http://www.w3.org/Style/CSS10/"><img src="Cascading%20Style%20Sheets_files/banner-w3c-white.png" alt="CSS10" style="height: 2.1em;"></a>

